y id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Widget / HeadlineWidget Settings'=>'Impostazioni del widget','Backend / Service Group / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> configured.'=>'Non è stato configurato alcun <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Widget / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Widget">Widget</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare tutte le impostazioni del <translation-key id="Widget">Widget</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite.','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineReset Default Service Groups'=>'Ripristinare i gruppi di servizi predefiniti','Backend / Widget / Select OptionBottom Left'=>'In basso a sinistra','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Groups'=>'Gruppi di servizi','Backend / Widget / Select OptionBottom Right'=>'In basso a destra','Backend / Service Groups / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> remain unchanged.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare i <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite. I <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key> personalizzati rimangono invariati.','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Init / Plugin LinksDashboard'=>'Bacheca','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Init / Plugin LinksLicense'=>'Licenza','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlinePosition'=>'Posizione','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Settings / FieldsBar'=>'Barra','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key>?','Backend / Settings / FieldsFoo'=>'Foo','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> can be grouped thematically into <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> which are displayed to the visitor. Unused <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> can be disabled, new ones can be added. The <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key> cannot be deactivated. All <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> belonging to <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key> are always issued. An active <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is only displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>, if at least one active <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is assigned to it.'=>'I <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> possono essere raggruppati tematicamente in <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key> che vengono mostrati al visitatore. I <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key> non utilizzati possono essere disattivati e se ne possono aggiungere di nuovi. Il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Necessari</translation-key> non può essere disattivato. Tutti i <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> appartenenti a <translation-key id="Essential">Necessari</translation-key> vengono sempre erogati. Un <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> attivo viene mostrato nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> solo se ad esso è assegnato almeno un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> attivo.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is active and displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> è attivo e viene mostrato nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>. Non disponibile per il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Necessari</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. Not available for default <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. Non disponibile per i <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key> predefiniti.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Modifica il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> è inattivo e non viene mostrato nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>. Non disponibile per il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Necessari</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageYour configured domain is different from the website domain. The setting may be incorrect and will cause the Dialog to reappear on each page.'=>'Il dominio configurato è diverso da quello del sito web. L\'impostazione potrebbe essere errata e causare la ricomparsa della finestra di dialogo in ogni pagina.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageYou have enabled <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> in your browser therefore you will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'Hai abilitato <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Non tracciare&quot;</translation-key> nel tuo browser, pertanto non vedrai la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> sul tuo sito web.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageIf this option is active, most likely all visits will be counted as "Direct visits" and the origin will be lost. We therefore recommend not to activate this option!'=>'Se questa opzione è attiva, molto probabilmente tutte le visite saranno conteggiate come "visite dirette" e l\'origine andrà persa. Consigliamo pertanto di non attivare questa opzione!','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageOnly activate this option if you need to reload your page after consent. Less than 1 &#37; of all <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> customers need this option enabled. If you don\'t know if you need this option, you won\'t need it.'=>'Attiva questa opzione solo se hai bisogno di ricaricare la pagina dopo il consenso. Meno di 1 &#37; di tutti i clienti di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> necessitano che questa opzione sia abilitata. Se non sai se hai bisogno di questa opzione, non ne avrai bisogno.','Backend / Settings / BreadcrumbGeneral Settings'=>'Impostazioni generali','Backend / Settings / LabelAggregate Consents'=>'Aggregare i consensi','Backend / Settings / LabelAutomatic Domain and Path Detection'=>'Rilevamento automatico del dominio e del percorso','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Stato di Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / LabelDomain'=>'Dominio','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Lifetime in Days'=>'Durata del cookie in giorni','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Lifetime in Days - Essential Only'=>'Durata del cookie in giorni - Solo Necessari','Backend / Settings / LabelPath'=>'Percorso','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Attributo Secure</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Version'=>'Versione del cookie','Backend / Settings / LabelCookies for Bots/Crawlers'=>'Cookie per bot/crawler','Backend / Settings / LabelCross Cookie Domains'=>'Cookie interdomio - Domini','Backend / Plugin Settings / LabelDisplay Meta Box'=>'Mostrare il meta box','Backend / Settings / LabelReload After Opt-in'=>'Ricaricare dopo l\'opt-in','Backend / Settings / LabelReload After Opt-out'=>'Ricaricare dopo l\'opt-out','Backend / Settings / LabelSetup Mode'=>'Modalità di configurazione','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Update Cookie Version &amp; Force Re-Selection</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Aggiornare la versione del cookie &amp; Forzare la riselezione</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / HeadlineCookie Settings'=>'Impostazioni del cookie','Backend / Settings / HeadlineGeneral Settings'=>'Impostazioni generali','Backend / Settings / HeadlineReset General Settings'=>'Ripristinare le impostazioni generali','Backend / Settings / HintAggregate the consents of all WordPress sites in one table.'=>'Aggrega i consensi di tutti i siti WordPress in un\'unica tabella.','Backend / Settings / Hint<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to automatically detect domain and path.'=>'<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> cerca di rilevare automaticamente il dominio e il percorso.','Backend / Settings / HintActivates <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> on your website. Displays the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and blocks iframes and other external media.'=>'Attiva <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> sul tuo sito web. Mostra la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> e blocca iframe e altri media esterni.','Backend / Settings / HintSpecify the domain scheme for which the cookie is valid. Example: If you enter <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> the cookie is also valid for subdomains like <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Specifica lo schema del dominio per il quale il cookie è valido. Esempio: se inserisci <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> il cookie è valido anche per sottodomini come <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintNumber of days until the visitor is asked again for their consent. Remember to adjust the <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Cookie Lifetime</translation-key> information of the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Numero di giorni prima che al visitatore venga nuovamente chiesto il consenso. Ricordati di modificare le informazioni sulla <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Durata del cookie</translation-key> del <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> in <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintThe path for which the cookie is valid. Default path: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>'=>'Il percorso per il quale il cookie è valido. Percorso predefinito: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>','Backend / Settings / HintThe <translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">SameSite attribute</translation-key> defines how the browser should handle cookies in cross-site requests. We recommend using the <strong>Lax</strong> option.'=>'L\'<translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">Attributo SameSite</translation-key> definisce il modo in cui il browser deve gestire i cookie nelle richieste tra siti. Consigliamo di utilizzare l\'opzione <strong>Lax</strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintA cookie with the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key> is sent to the server only in case of an encrypted request via the HTTPS protocol.'=>'Un cookie con l\'<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Attributo Secure</translation-key> viene inviato al server solo in caso di richiesta crittografata tramite il protocollo HTTPS.','Backend / Settings / HintShows the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Increases with activating <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Update Cookie Version &amp; Force Re-Selection</translation-key>.'=>'Mostra la versione del cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Aumenta con l\'attivazione di <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Aggiornare la versione del cookie &amp; Forzare la riselezione</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintA bot/crawler is treated like a visitor who accepted all <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>.'=>'Un bot/crawler viene trattato come un visitatore che ha accettato tutti i <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintAdd one URL per line. Insert WordPress Address (URL). URL must end with <strong>/</strong>. Consent will be shared between websites.'=>'Aggiungi un URL per riga. Inserisci l\'indirizzo WordPress (URL). L\'URL deve terminare con <strong>/</strong>. I consensi saranno condivisi tra i siti web.','Backend / Settings / HintDisplay the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> on the selected post types. The <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> allows you to add custom JavaScript on specific pages.'=>'Mostra il <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> sui tipi di articoli selezionati. Il <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> ti consente di aggiungere JavaScript personalizzato su pagine specifiche.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor saves their consent.'=>'Se abilitato, il sito web verrà ricaricato dopo che il visitatore avrà salvato il proprio consenso.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor opt out.'=>'Se abilitato, il sito web verrà ricaricato dopo l\'opt-out del visitatore.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Settings">Settings</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare tutte le <translation-key id="Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite.','Backend / Settings / HintA visitor with active <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> setting will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> automatically selects the <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accept Only Essential</translation-key> option.'=>'Un visitatore con l\'impostazione <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Non tracciare&quot;</translation-key> attiva non vedrà la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> seleziona automaticamente l\'opzione <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accetta solo i necessari</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintWith Setup Mode enabled, you can test your setup without having to enable <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>. Only you will see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'Con la modalità configurazione attivata, puoi testare la tua configurazione senza dover abilitare lo <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Stato di Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Solo tu vedrai la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> sul tuo sito web.','Backend / Settings / HintUpdates the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. This will cause the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> to reappear for visitors who have already selected an option.'=>'Aggiorna la versione del cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. In questo modo la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> riapparirà per i visitatori che hanno già selezionato un\'opzione.','Backend / Settings / TextVersion'=>'Versione','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you have to aggregate the consent:'=>'Quando è necessario aggregare il consenso:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using only the domain (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) and the other site a subdomain (e.g. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- se un sito utilizza solo il dominio (ad es. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) e l\'altro sito un sottodominio (ad es. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using the root folder <strong>/</strong> and the other site a subfolder (e.g. <strong>/shop</strong>)'=>'- se un sito utilizza la cartella principale <strong>/</strong> e l\'altro sito una sottocartella (ad es. <strong>/shop</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you can separate the consent:'=>'Quando puoi separare il consenso:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different domains (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) or different subdomains (e.g. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- se tutti i siti utilizzano domini diversi (ad es. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> e <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) o sottodomini diversi (ad es. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> e <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different subfolders (e.g. <strong>/en</strong> and <strong>/de</strong>)'=>'- se tutti i siti utilizzano sottocartelle diverse (ad es. <strong>/en</strong> e <strong>/de</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe visitor\'s consent is transferred to all specified domains and WordPress installations, provided the websites are set up in the same way (<translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> IDs must match). Any consent or modification by the visitor will be shared with the specified domains.'=>'Il consenso del visitatore viene trasferito a tutti i domini e alle installazioni WordPress specificate, a condizione che i siti web siano impostati allo stesso modo (<translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> e gli ID del <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> devono combaciare). Qualsiasi consenso o modifica da parte del visitatore sarà condivisa con i domini specificati.','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>More information about <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Ulteriori informazioni su <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cookie interdominio - Domini</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineAggregate Consents'=>'Aggregare i consensi','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cookie interdominio - Domini</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Cookie Version?'=>'Che cos\'è la versione del cookie?','Backend / Plugin Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Meta Box?'=>'Che cos\'è il meta box?','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is assigned a version number. It is used to ask the visitor again for their consent if changes have been made to the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>. If the version number in the cookie differs from the current version number, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> appears to the visitor.'=>'Al cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> viene assegnato un numero di versione. Viene utilizzato per chiedere nuovamente il consenso al visitatore se sono state apportate modifiche ai <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>. Se il numero di versione del cookie è diverso da quello attuale, al visitatore viene mostrata la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Plugin Settings / Things to know / TextIf active the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> is displayed in the selected post types. This allows you to execute code (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key>) on the page and e.g. trigger a conversion pixel.'=>'Se attivo, il <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> viene mostrato nei tipi di articoli selezionati. Ciò ti consente di eseguire codici (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcode</translation-key>) sulla pagina e, ad esempio, di attivare un pixel di conversione.','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Script Blocker / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Content blocker JavaScript Globale','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelHandles'=>'Handle','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelPhrases'=>'Frasi','Backend / Script Blocker / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Tag script per l\'opt-in del servizio','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Configuration'=>'Configurazione dello style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Information'=>'Informazioni sullo style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Settings'=>'Impostazioni dello style blocker','Backend / Script Blocker / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Se la tua intenzione è quella di sbloccare <translation-key id="Styles">Stili</translation-key> precedentemente bloccati al momento dello sblocco di un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, inserisci il JavaScript fornito nel campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> delle tue impostazioni del <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere impostato. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere lungo almeno 3 caratteri e può contenere solo: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Il nome dello <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blocker / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Per consentire lo sblocco di <translation-key id="Styles">Stili</translation-key> precedentemente bloccati tramite il consenso dell\'utente per un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>, inserisci il seguente tag script nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> all\'interno del tuo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block stylesheets and style-tags.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>. Se lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> è disattivato, non bloccherà i fogli di stile e i tag.','Backend / Style Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Non è stato configurato alcuno <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blockers / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Style blocker','Backend / Style Blockers / HeadlineStyle Blockers'=>'Style blocker','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineHandles'=>'Handle','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlinePhrases'=>'Frasi','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key>?','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Indipendente dalla lingua','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key> sono configurati in modo indipendente per tutte le lingue.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> that, for example, embed <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> to load external fonts like <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.'=>'La sezione <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key> ti consente di bloccare <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> da <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugin</translation-key> che, ad esempio, incorporano <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> per caricare font esterni come <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Una volta creato uno <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fornisce un JavaScript di sblocco che può essere inserito nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> di un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Il <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> viene sbloccato una volta che il visitatore dà il suo consenso al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> è abilitato e impedisce attivamente l\'esecuzione dei <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> se le <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o le <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key> corrispondono a un termine configurato nel sistema.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>. Non disponibile per uno <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> installato tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Modifica lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> are executed without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> è inattivo e consente l\'esecuzione di tutti i <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> senza filtri o restrizioni basate su <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key>.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageConnecting to the API failed. Please check that WordPress has access to the Internet or retry later.'=>'Connessione all\'API non riuscita. Verificare che WordPress abbia accesso a Internet o riprovare più tardi.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageMoving the database file failed.'=>'Spostamento del file di database non riuscito.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessagePlease enable GeoIP before downloading the database.'=>'Attivare il GeoIP prima di scaricare il database.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageThe database was successfully updated.'=>'Il database è stato aggiornato con successo.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageYou already have the most up-to-date database.'=>'Hai già il database più aggiornato.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageUnpacking the database to the temporary folder failed. Please check if the temporary folder is writable and the PHP module ZIP is installed.'=>'Decompressione del database nella cartella temporanea non riuscita. Verificare che la cartella temporanea sia scrivibile e che il modulo PHP ZIP sia installato.','Backend / Model Localization / ModelCompatibility Patch'=>'Patch di compatibilità','Backend / Model Localization / ModelContent Blocker'=>'Content blocker','Backend / Model Localization / ModelProvider'=>'Provider','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key> cookies are used to analyze user behavior on the website and to optimize the website based on the results.'=>'I cookie di <translation-key id="Tracking">Tracciamento</translation-key> sono utilizzati per analizzare il comportamento degli utenti sul sito web e per ottimizzare il sito in base ai risultati.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>: Choose where information is stored in the browser. <translation-key id="HTTP">HTTP</translation-key> cookies are commonly used, alternatives like <translation-key id="Local-Storage">Local Storage</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Session-Storage">Session Storage</translation-key> do not possess predetermined lifetimes.'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Tipo</translation-key>: scegli dove vengono memorizzate le informazioni nel browser. I cookie <translation-key id="HTTP">HTTP</translation-key> sono comunemente utilizzati, mentre alternative come l\'<translation-key id="Local-Storage">Archiviazione locale</translation-key> o l\'<translation-key id="Session-Storage">Archiviazione di sessione</translation-key> non hanno una durata predeterminata.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> selected.'=>'Non è stato selezionato alcun <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / AlertThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> selezionato non è disponibile nella lingua corrente.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> selezionato non esiste.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> selezionato non esiste.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> selezionato non è disponibile nella lingua corrente.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> selezionato non è disponibile nella lingua corrente.','Backend / Service / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Services / BreadcrumbServices'=>'Servizi','Backend / Services / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Services / LabelDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / Services / LabelFallback Code'=>'Codice di fallback','Backend / Services / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Services / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key>','Backend / Services / LabelOpt-out Code'=>'Codice per l\'opt-out','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Opt-out Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Shortcode per l\'opt-out</translation-key>','Backend / Services / LabelPosition'=>'Posizione','Backend / Services / LabelProvider List'=>'Elenco dei provider','Backend / Services / LabelService Group'=>'Gruppo di servizi','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Services / LabelStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Services / HeadlineHTML &amp; JavaScript'=>'HTML &amp; JavaScript','Backend / Services / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Informazioni sul provider','Backend / Services / HeadlineService Group Information'=>'Informazioni sul gruppo di servizi','Backend / Services / HeadlineService Information'=>'Informazioni sul servizio','Backend / Services / HeadlineService Settings'=>'Impostazioni del servizio','Backend / Services / HintExplain to your visitors what this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> does.'=>'Spiega ai tuoi visitatori cosa fa questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintThis code will always be executed.'=>'Questo codice verrà sempre eseguito.','Backend / Services / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere impostato. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere lungo almeno 3 caratteri e può contenere solo: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Services / HintInsert a name for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Inserisci un nome per questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintThis code is executed after the visitor has given their consent.'=>'Questo codice viene eseguito dopo che il visitatore ha dato il suo consenso.','Backend / Services / HintThis code is executed only if the visitor has previously consented and now chooses to opt out. It is executed once.'=>'Questo codice viene eseguito solo se il visitatore ha precedentemente acconsentito e ora sceglie di rinunciare. Viene eseguito una sola volta.','Backend / Services / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to display an opt-out option for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Utilizza questo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> per mostrare un\'opzione di opt-out per questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintDetermine the position where this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is displayed in its <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. Order follows natural numbers.'=>'Stabilisci la posizione in cui questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> viene mostrato nel suo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. L\'ordine segue i numeri naturali.','Backend / Services / HintA <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> must be linked to a <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. You may choose an existing <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> or establish a new one. Please note, the option to create a new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is available exclusively during the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> creation process within this view.'=>'Un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> deve essere collegato a un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Puoi scegliere un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> esistente o crearne uno nuovo. Nota che l\'opzione di creazione di un nuovo <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> è disponibile esclusivamente durante il processo di creazione del <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> in questa visualizzazione.','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is part of.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> di cui fa parte il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to unblock JavaScript or content when user opted-in for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Utilizza questo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> per sbloccare JavaScript o contenuti quando l\'utente ha effettuato l\'opt-in per questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. If enabled it is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Se abilitato (stato: ON), viene mostrato al visitatore nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'...blocca questo...','Backend / Services / Input PlaceholderNever'=>'Mai','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Durata','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Services</translation-key>).'=>'I <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> sono inclusi in questo pacchetto e sono necessari per il suo corretto funzionamento. Vengono installati quando clicchi sul pulsante <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installa</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstalla</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Aggiorna</translation-key>. Puoi individuarli in seguito utilizzando il nome e la chiave mostrati nella vista <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Servizi</translation-key>). ','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Finalità','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key>).'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key> sono inclusi in questo pacchetto e sono necessari per il suo corretto funzionamento. Vengono installati quando clicchi sul pulsante <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installa</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstalla</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Aggiorna</translation-key>. Puoi individuarli in seguito utilizzando il nome e la chiave mostrati nella vista <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blocker</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key>).','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineType'=>'Tipo','Backend / Library / NavigationAll'=>'Tutti','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIf you enable this option <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> searches and deletes cookies that match the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>). You can also use <strong>*</strong> to search for multiple names, e.g. if you enter the Name <strong><em>example_*</em></strong> <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will search and delete the cookies <strong><em>example_abc</em></strong> and <strong><em>example_xyz</em></strong>.'=>'Se abiliti questa opzione, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> cerca ed elimina i cookie che corrispondono al <translation-key id="Name">Nome</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Nome">Nome</translation-key>). Puoi anche utilizzare <strong>*</strong> per cercare più nomi, ad es. se inserisci il nome <strong><em>example_*</em>,</strong> <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> cercherà ed eliminerà i cookie <strong><em>example_abc</em></strong> e <strong><em>example_xyz</em></strong>.','Backend / Library / NavigationFilter'=>'Filtro','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThis function is mainly intended to delete session cookies set by third-party plugins via PHP. JavaScript cookies can also be deleted, but only if they belong to the same domain and do not have the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key>.'=>'Questa funzione serve principalmente a eliminare i cookie di sessione impostati da plugin di terze parti tramite PHP. Anche i cookie JavaScript possono essere eliminati, ma solo se appartengono allo stesso dominio e non hanno l\'<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Attributo Secure</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextExample: if the website operates under <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>, no cookie associated with <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> can be deleted.'=>'Esempio: se il sito web opera sotto <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>, nessun cookie associato a <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> può essere eliminato.','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content blocker</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextNamed cookies will be only set after consent by the visitor was given and the website was reloaded.'=>'I cookie menzionati verranno impostati solo dopo che è stato dato il consenso da parte del visitatore e il sito web è stato ricaricato.','Backend / Library / NavigationInstalled Packages'=>'Pacchetti installati','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Block-Cookies-Before-Consent">Block Cookies Before Consent</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Block-Cookies-Before-Consent">Bloccare i cookie prima del consenso</translation-key>','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blocker</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritize</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Prioritize">Dare la priorità</translation-key>','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> information?'=>'Qual è lo scopo delle informazioni sul <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>?','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineOpt-out Shortcode explained'=>'Spiegazione dello shortcode per l\'opt-out','Backend / Library / Input PlaceholderSearch'=>'Cerca','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'Spiegazione dello <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Library / Table HeadlineType'=>'Tipo','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to display an opt-out option for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> può essere utilizzato per mostrare un\'opzione di opt-out per questo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> is loaded in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> and is executed before the page is fully loaded.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> viene caricato in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> e viene eseguito prima del caricamento completo della pagina.','Backend / Library / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThis function cannot be combined with unblock code from a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Questa funzione non può essere combinata con il codice di sblocco da un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / TextAre you sure you want to uninstall the package?'=>'Sei sicuro di voler disinstallare il pacchetto?','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Per motivi di conformità legale, ogni <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> deve essere collegato a un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> specifico.','Backend / Library / TextPackage'=>'Pacchetto','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> section (found under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key>), you will find more information and also have the option to edit or create new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> entries.'=>'Nella sezione <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> (disponibile in <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Provider</translation-key>), troverai ulteriori informazioni e avrai anche la possibilità di modificare o creare nuove voci <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / TextRecommended'=>'Consigliato','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease activate your license key first. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Click here</a> to enter your license key.'=>'Attiva prima la tua chiave di licenza. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Clicca qui</a> per inserire la tua chiave di licenza.','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease enter your license key to receive updates.'=>'Inserisci la tua chiave di licenza per ricevere gli aggiornamenti.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> once the visitor has given consent to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> può essere utilizzato per eseguire un codice personalizzato associato a questo tipo di <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>, una volta che il visitatore ha dato il suo consenso al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Può essere utilizzato, ad esempio, per bloccare il codice di un pixel di conversione.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license key is not valid.'=>'La tua chiave di licenza non è valida.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> for example can be used in the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. You can find it for example in <translation-key id="Posts">Posts</translation-key> &raquo; <em><translation-key id="Your-Post">Your Post</translation-key></em> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Custom-Code">Custom Code</translation-key>.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>, ad esempio, può essere utilizzato nel <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Puoi trovarlo ad esempio in <translation-key id="Posts">Articoli</translation-key> &raquo; <em><translation-key id="Your-Post">Il tuo articolo</translation-key></em> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Custom-Code">Codice personalizzato</translation-key>.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license request is not valid.'=>'La tua richiesta di licenza non è valida.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> are not available until the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is created.'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcode</translation-key> non sono disponibili fino alla creazione del <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / LabelAsynchronous Opt-out Code'=>'Codice opt-out asincrono','Backend / Services / LabelBlock Cookies Before Consent'=>'Bloccare i cookie prima del consenso','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritize</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Prioritize">Dare la priorità</translation-key>','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Opt-out Code</translation-key> contains asynchronous JavaScript code that needs to executed to finish the Opt-out.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Codice opt-out</translation-key> contiene un codice JavaScript asincrono che deve essere eseguito per completare l\'opt-out.','Backend / Services / HintIf enabled, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to block cookies with the names from <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Cookie Name</translation-key> until consent is given.'=>'Se abilitato (stato: ON) <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tenta di bloccare i cookie con i nomi da <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Nome del cookie</translation-key> finché non viene dato il consenso.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense information refreshed successfully.'=>'Le informazioni sulla licenza sono state aggiornate con successo.','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> is loaded in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> and is executed before the page is fully loaded.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> viene caricato in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> e viene eseguito prima del caricamento completo della pagina.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense registered successfully.'=>'Licenza registrata con successo.','Backend / Service Location / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Location">Location</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Location">Indirizzo</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense removed successfully.'=>'Licenza rimossa con successo.','Backend / Service Location / ButtonAdd Location'=>'Aggiungi un indirizzo','Backend / Service Location / LabelHostname'=>'Nome host','Backend / License / BreadcrumbLicense'=>'Licenza','Backend / Service Location / LabelPath'=>'Percorso','Backend / License / Button TitleRefresh License Information'=>'Aggiorna le informazioni sulla licenza','Backend / Service Location / Headline<translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Locations">Indirizzi</translation-key>','Backend / License / Button TitleRemove License'=>'Rimuovi la licenza','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Nome host','Backend / License / LabelCloud Scans'=>'Scansioni cloud','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Percorso','Backend / License / LabelConfirm Refresh'=>'Confermare l\'aggiornamento','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Che cos\'è un <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Key'=>'Chiave di licenza','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Locations">Indirizzi</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Name'=>'Nome della licenza','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key> è il nome di dominio del sito web. Ad esempio, se l\'URL del sito web è <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, il <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key> è <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / License / LabelLicense Status'=>'Stato della licenza','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextIt may happen that an embedded <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> on your website does not set a cookie, but a connection to a foreign domain is established. Therefore, it is advisable to record this domain here and thus name the service responsible for it, so that interested visitors can understand why this external connection occurs.'=>'Può accadere che un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> incorporato nel tuo sito web non imposti un cookie, ma che venga stabilita una connessione a un dominio estero. È quindi consigliabile registrare questo dominio e dare un nome al servizio responsabile, in modo che i visitatori interessati possano capire il motivo di questa connessione esterna.','Backend / License / LabelValid Until'=>'Valida fino','Backend / Service Option / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Option">Option</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessuna <translation-key id="Option">Opzione</translation-key> configurata.','Backend / License / LabelMax Websites'=>'Massimo numero di siti web','Backend / Service Option / ButtonAdd Option'=>'Aggiungi un\'opzione','Backend / License / LabelRefresh'=>'Aggiornare','Backend / Service Option / LabelDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / License / Headline<translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Remove-License">Rimuovere la licenza</translation-key>','Backend / Service Option / Headline<translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Options">Opzioni</translation-key>','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License'=>'La tua licenza','Backend / Service Option / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License Information'=>'Informazioni sulla tua licenza','Backend / Service Option / Table Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Tipo</translation-key>','Backend / License / HintEnter your License Key.'=>'Inserisci la tua chiave di licenza.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Options">Opzioni</translation-key>?','Backend / License / HintPlease confirm that you want to remove your license data from this website. After the license data is removed you are able to enter your new license key.'=>'Conferma che desideri rimuovere i dati della tua licenza da questo sito web. Dopo aver rimosso i dati della licenza, potrai inserire la tua nuova chiave di licenza.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextWith <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> you can provide more information about the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. There are six <translation-key id="Types">Types</translation-key> to choose from and you can add as many <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> as you like.'=>'Tramite <translation-key id="Options">Opzioni</translation-key> puoi fornire ulteriori informazioni sul <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Esistono sei <translation-key id="Types">Tipi</translation-key> tra cui scegliere e puoi aggiungere tutte le <translation-key id="Options">Opzioni</translation-key> che desideri.','Backend / License / TextYour license has expired.'=>'La tua licenza è scaduta.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextFor example, you could select the &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Location Processing</translation-key>&quot; <translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key> and add <strong>United States of America</strong> as description if the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> processes data in the United States.'=>'Ad esempio, potresti selezionare il <translation-key id="Type">Tipo</translation-key> &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Luogo del trattamento</translation-key>&quot; e aggiungere <strong>Stati Uniti d\'America</strong> come descrizione se il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> tratta dati negli Stati Uniti.','Backend / License / TextYour license is valid.'=>'La tua licenza è valida.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / License / Things to know / HeadlineTransferring a license key to a new website'=>'Trasferire una chiave di licenza a un nuovo sito web','Backend / License / Things to know / TextYou can use the <translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key> option to remove the license from this website, or you can visit our <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key> and remove the license from there.'=>'Puoi utilizzare l\'opzione <translation-key id="Remove-License">Rimuovere la licenza</translation-key> per rimuovere la licenza da questo sito web oppure visita il nostro <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Portale clienti</translation-key> e rimuovi la licenza da lì.','Backend / License / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Portale clienti</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Local Scanner / TextAn error has occurred. Please check your browser\'s console for an error message. If the issue persists even after trying again and switching to <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>, kindly reach out to our support team for assistance.'=>'Si è verificato un errore. Controlla se sulla console del tuo browser è presente un messaggio di errore. Se il problema persiste anche dopo aver riprovato e dopo aver scelto la <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Modalità di scansione</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Manuale</translation-key>, contatta la nostra assistenza per ricevere aiuto. ','Backend / Services / HeadlineReset Default Services'=>'Ripristinare i servizi predefiniti','Backend / Local Scanner / ButtonRun scan'=>'Esegui la scansione','Backend / Services / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare tutte le impostazioni del <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite. I tuoi <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> personalizzati e i <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> installati tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key> non vengono reimpostati.','Backend / Local Scanner / LabelPage to scan'=>'Pagina da scansionare','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Modalità di scansione</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePosition'=>'Posizione','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Frase di ricerca</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Progress'=>'Avanzamento della scansione','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>?','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Settings'=>'Impostazioni di scansione','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Local Scanner / HintThe string <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is looking for. Separate multiple entries with a comma.'=>'La stringa che <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> sta cercando. Separa più voci con una virgola.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section you can document the use of services and their cookies for your visitors, as well as integrate JavaScripts, such as Google Analytics.'=>'Nella sezione <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> puoi documentare per i tuoi visitatori l\'uso dei servizi e dei relativi cookie, nonché integrare JavaScript, come Google Analytics.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextBecause <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> uses the opt-in process, JavaScripts are only executed after the visitor has given their consent to the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Poiché <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> utilizza il processo opt-in, i JavaScript vengono eseguiti solo dopo che il visitatore ha dato il proprio consenso al <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> o al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Scan Modes</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Modalità di scansione</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is active and displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> è attivo e viene mostrato nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>. Non disponibile per il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Current-User">Current User</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as the currently logged in user. This may affect the results if the user has different rights than a guest user.'=>'<translation-key id="Current-User">Utente corrente</translation-key>:<br>la scansione viene eseguita come utente attualmente connesso. Ciò può influire sui risultati se l\'utente ha diritti diversi da quelli di un utente ospite.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Non disponibile per il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineFor example: Some plugins do not embed tracking JavaScript for users with the role of an administrator.'=>'Ad esempio: alcuni plugin non incorporano il tracciamento di JavaScript per gli utenti con il ruolo di amministratore.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Modifica il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Guest">Guest</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as a guest user. This is the default setting.'=>'<translation-key id="Guest">Ospite</translation-key>:<br>la scansione viene eseguita come utente ospite. Questa è l\'impostazione predefinita.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> è inattivo e non viene mostrato nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>. Non disponibile per il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>:<br>When you use this mode, a signed URL is provided that you can use to run the scan by clicking on it. This is useful if the scan cannot be performed due to a server configuration or if your website is not accessible from the outside (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Local Environment</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Staging Environment</translation-key>), for example.'=>'<translation-key id="Manual">Manuale</translation-key>:<br>quando utilizzi questa modalità, viene fornito un URL firmato che puoi usare per eseguire la scansione facendo clic su di esso. Ciò è utile se la scansione non può essere eseguita a causa di una configurazione del server o se il tuo sito web non è accessibile dall\'esterno (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Ambiente locale</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Ambiente di staging</translation-key>), ad esempio.','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Local Scanner / Alert MessageNo scan result available.'=>'Non è disponibile alcun risultato di scansione.','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbService Groups'=>'Gruppi di servizi','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Handle corrispondenti</translation-key>','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Tag corrispondenti</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Handle non corrispondenti</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Tag non corrispondenti</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Local Scanner / HintSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Specifica il nome dell\'oggetto che deve essere presente per l\'esecuzione dello script della colonna <strong>Tag</strong>. I caratteri ammessi sono $, _, lettere (sia maiuscole che minuscole) e numeri. Il primo carattere deve essere $, _ o una lettera, mentre i caratteri successivi possono includere anche numeri.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPosition'=>'Posizione','Backend / Local Scanner / HintEnter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'Inserisci una stringa univoca trovata nel <strong>Tag</strong> per bloccare lo script. Dovrebbe essere abbastanza univoca da non essere trovata anche in altri JavaScript.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPre-selected'=>'Preselezionato','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineBlock'=>'Bloccare','Backend / Service Groups / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Information'=>'Informazioni sul gruppo di servizi','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Frase</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Settings'=>'Impostazioni del gruppo di servizi','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineTag'=>'Tag','Backend / Service Groups / HintEnter a description for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Inserisci una descrizione per questo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. Viene mostrata al visitatore nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineType'=>'Tipo','Backend / Service Groups / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere impostato. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere lungo almeno 3 caratteri e può contenere solo: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineURL'=>'URL','Backend / Service Groups / HintChoose a name for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Scegli un nome per questo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. Viene mostrato al visitatore nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the JavaScript files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> vengono utilizzati per identificare i file JavaScript caricati sul tuo sito web. Ad esempio, i <translation-key id="Themes">Temi</translation-key> e i <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugin</translation-key> installati utilizzano la funzione WordPress <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> per definire gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintDetermine the position where this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is displayed. Order follows natural numbers.'=>'Stabilisci la posizione in cui viene visualizzato il <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. L\'ordine segue i numeri naturali.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> sono utilizzati per identificare i file <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> caricati sul tuo sito web. Ad esempio, i <translation-key id="Themes">Temi</translation-key> e i <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugin</translation-key> installati utilizzano la funzione di WordPress <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> per definire gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintIf enabled, this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is pre-selected in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. The visitor can de-select it.'=>'Se abilitato (stato: ON), questo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> viene preselezionato nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>. Il visitatore può deselezionarlo.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Handle corrispondenti</translation-key>:<br>sono gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> che corrispondono alla tua <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Frase di ricerca</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to unblock JavaScript or content when user opted-in for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Utilizza questo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> per sbloccare JavaScript o contenuti quando l\'utente ha effettuato l\'opt-in per questo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Handle non corrispondenti</translation-key>:<br>si tratta di <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> che non corrispondono a una <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Frase di ricerca</translation-key>, ma che sono stati trovati durante la scansione e potrebbero essere rilevanti.','Backend / Service Groups / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. If enabled it is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. Se abilitato (stato: ON), viene mostrato al visitatore nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> explained'=>'Spiegazione degli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> ','Backend / Service Groups / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'...blocca questo...','Backend / Local Scanner / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Spiegazione dei campi di input','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'Spiegazione dello <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> explained'=>'Spiegazione dei <translation-key id="Tags">Tag</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code once the visitor has given consent to a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> può essere utilizzato per eseguire un codice personalizzato una volta che il visitatore ha dato il consenso a un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> associato a questo tipo di <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key>. Può essere utilizzato, ad esempio, per bloccare il codice di un pixel di conversione.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when JavaScript is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose.'=>'I <translation-key id="Tags">Tag</translation-key> si riferiscono a tag <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> che non hanno un <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key> associato, il che può verificarsi quando JavaScript viene incorporato direttamente nel codice HTML del tuo sito web, ignorando la funzione dedicata di WordPress generalmente utilizzata a questo scopo','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags and <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose.'=>'I <translation-key id="Tags">Tag</translation-key> si riferiscono a tag <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> e a tag <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> che non hanno un <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key> associato, il che può verificarsi quando <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> viene incorporato direttamente nel codice HTML del tuo sito web, ignorando la funzione dedicata di WordPress generalmente utilizzata a questo scopo','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Tag corrispondenti</translation-key>:<br>si tratta di <translation-key id="Tags">Tag</translation-key> che corrispondono alla tua <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Frase di ricerca</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Tag non corrispondenti</translation-key>:<br>si tratta di <translation-key id="Tags">Tag</translation-key> che non corrispondono a una <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Frase di ricerca</translation-key>, ma che sono stati trovati durante la scansione e potrebbero essere rilevanti.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Frase</translation-key>:<br>inserisci una stringa univoca trovata nel <strong>Tag</strong> per bloccare lo script. Dovrebbe essere sufficientemente univoca da non essere trovata anche in altri JavaScript.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>This feature is optional and ensures that once the JavaScript is unblocked, it does not execute until the object specified in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> column is present on the website. This capability facilitates the resolution of race condition issues.'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>questa funzionalità è opzionale e garantisce che, una volta sbloccato, il codice JavaScript non venga eseguito finché l\'oggetto specificato nella colonna <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> non è presente sul sito web. Questa funzionalità facilita la risoluzione di problemi di race condition.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Specifica il nome dell\'oggetto che deve essere presente per l\'esecuzione dello script dalla colonna <strong>Tag</strong>. I caratteri ammessi sono $, _, lettere (sia maiuscole che minuscole) e numeri. Il primo carattere deve essere $, _ o una lettera, mentre i caratteri successivi possono includere anche numeri.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineExample:'=>'Esempio:','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineThe example initiates loading an external library and concurrently calls the <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> function. This could induce a race condition issue since, when <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is invoked, the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library—responsible for providing this method—might not yet be fully loaded.'=>'L\'esempio avvia il caricamento di una libreria esterna e chiama contemporaneamente la funzione <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. Questo potrebbe indurre un problema di race condition poiché, quando viene richiamata la funzione <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>, il file <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong>, responsabile della fornitura di questo metodo, potrebbe non essere ancora completamente caricato.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineTo mitigate this race condition, block both the script tag that loads the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library and the script tag that calls <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. For the script tag where <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is called, enter <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> field.'=>'Per mitigare questa race condition, blocca sia il tag script che carica la libreria <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> sia il tag script che richiama 
 <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. Per il tag script in cui <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> viene chiamato, inserisci <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> nel campo <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineIf the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is now unblocked, the script-tag containing <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> will not execute until the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> has completely loaded.'=>'Se lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è ora sbloccato, il tag script che contiene <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> non verrà eseguito finché il file <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> non sarà stato completamente caricato.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags or <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Frase</translation-key>:<br>inserisci una stringa univoca trovata nel <strong>Tag</strong> per bloccare il <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>. Deve essere abbastanza univoca da non essere trovata anche in altri tag <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> o <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong>.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not found in the JavaScript code on the left side.'=>'La frase non si trova nel codice JavaScript sul lato sinistro.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not unique and overlaps with a phrase for another JavaScript.'=>'La frase non è univoca e si sovrappone a quella di un altro JavaScript.','Backend / Log / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Log">Log</translation-key> could not be found.'=>'Non è stato possibile trovare il <translation-key id="Log">Log</translation-key>. ','Backend / Log / Breadcrumb<translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Logs">Log</translation-key>','Backend / Log / BreadcrumbDetails'=>'Dettagli','Backend / Log / HeadlineProcess History'=>'Cronologia del processo','Backend / Log / FieldBacktrace'=>'Backtrace','Backend / Log / FieldContext'=>'Contesto','Backend / Log / FieldLevel'=>'Livello','Backend / Log / FieldMessage'=>'Messaggio','Backend / Log / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key> found.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Logs">Log</translation-key> trovato.','Backend / Log / Headline<translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Logs">Log</translation-key>','Backend / Log / PlaceholderSearch Process ID, Level or Message'=>'Cerca ID processo, livello o messaggio','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineHas backtrace'=>'Ha una backtrace','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineHas context'=>'Ha un contesto','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineCreated at'=>'Creato il','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineLevel'=>'Livello','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineMessage'=>'Messaggio','Backend / MetaBox / Field<translation-key id="Custom-Code">Custom Code</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Custom-Code">Codice personalizzato</translation-key>','Backend / MetaBox / HeadlineBorlabs Cookie - Meta Box'=>'Borlabs Cookie - Meta box','Backend / MetaBox / HintThe code you enter here will only run on this page. Extend your code by wrapping it with our blocking <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> to ensure that it only executes after you\'ve received consent. This functionality proves useful in scenarios such as needing to trigger a conversion pixel exclusively on this page.'=>'Il codice che inserisci qui verrà eseguito solo su questa pagina. Estendi il tuo codice avvolgendolo con i nostri <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcode</translation-key> di blocco per garantire che venga eseguito solo dopo aver ricevuto il consenso. Questa funzionalità si rivela utile in scenari quali la necessità di attivare un pixel di conversione esclusivamente su questa pagina.','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbProviders'=>'Provider','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Providers / LabelAddress'=>'Indirizzo','Backend / Providers / LabelCookie URL'=>'URL del cookie','Backend / Providers / LabelDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">ID vendor IAB</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Providers / LabelOpt-out URL'=>'URL per l\'opt-out','Backend / Providers / LabelPartners'=>'Partner','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy URL</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">URL informativa sulla privacy</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Informazioni sul provider','Backend / Providers / LabelYou can optionally provide the <translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key> to add information about an IAB Vendor that is not part of the IAB TCF standard.'=>'Facoltativamente, puoi fornire l\'<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">ID vendor IAB</translation-key> per aggiungere informazioni su un vendor IAB che non fa parte dello standard TCF di IAB.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Providers">Provider</translation-key>?','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Per motivi di conformità legale, ogni <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> deve essere collegato a un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> specifico.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is the company that delivers the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (e.g., Google Analytics) or the content (e.g., YouTube videos).'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> è la società che fornisce il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> (ad es. Google Analytics) o il contenuto (ad es. i video di YouTube).','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextVisitors should receive clear information about the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsible for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or blocked content.'=>'I visitatori devono ricevere informazioni chiare sul <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsabile del <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> o del contenuto bloccato.','Backend / Providers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProviders'=>'Provider','Backend / Providers / HeadlineReset Default Providers'=>'Ripristinare i provider predefiniti','Backend / Providers / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare i <translation-key id="Providers">Provider</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite. I tuoi <translation-key id="Providers">Provider</translation-key> personalizzati e i <translation-key id="Providers">Provider</translation-key> installati tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key> non vengono reimpostati.','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Owner of this website</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Non disponibile per il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Proprietario di questo sito web</translation-key>.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Modifica il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbScript Blockers'=>'Script blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Script Blockers / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Content blocker JavaScript Globale','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelHandles'=>'Handle','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Script Blockers / Label<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelPhrases'=>'Frasi','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Tag script per l\'opt-in del servizio','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Configuration'=>'Configurazione dello script blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Information'=>'Informazioni sullo script blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Settings'=>'Impostazioni dello script blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked JavaScripts upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Se la tua intenzione è sbloccare JavaScript precedentemente bloccati dopo aver sbloccato un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, inserisci il JavaScript fornito nel campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> delle impostazioni del <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere impostato. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere lungo almeno 3 caratteri e può contenere solo: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Il nome dello <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked JavaScripts through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Per consentire lo sblocco di JavaScript precedentemente bloccati tramite il consenso dell\'utente per un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>, inserisci il tag script che segue nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> all\'interno del tuo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block JavaScript.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>. Se lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è disattivato, non bloccherà JavaScript.','Backend / Script Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Non è stato configurato alcuno <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blockers'=>'Script blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="On-Exist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="On-Exist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blocker</translation-key>?','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Indipendente dalla lingua','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blocker</translation-key> sono configurati in modo indipendente per tutte le lingue.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block JavaScripts from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> whose JavaScript you can\'t enter into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'La sezione <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script blocker</translation-key> ti consente di bloccare i JavaScript da <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugin</translation-key> il cui JavaScript non può essere inserito nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> di un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The JavaScript becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Una volta creato uno <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fornisce un JavaScript di sblocco che può essere inserito nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> di un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Il JavaScript viene sbloccato una volta che il visitatore dà il suo consenso al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThis usually allows you to continue using your favorite plugins, but their JavaScript will only run when a visitor gave consent.'=>'Questo di solito ti consente di continuare a utilizzare i tuoi plugin preferiti, ma il loro JavaScript verrà eseguito solo quando il visitatore ha dato il suo consenso.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents JavaScript execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è abilitato e impedisce attivamente l\'esecuzione di JavaScript se gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o le <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key> corrispondono a un termine configurato nel sistema.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>. Non disponibile per uno <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> installato tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Modificare lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all JavaScript to execute without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è inattivo e consente l\'esecuzione di tutti i JavaScript senza filtri o restrizioni basate su <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Cookie / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Service Cookie / ButtonAdd Cookie'=>'Aggiungi un cookie','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldLifetime'=>'Durata','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldName'=>'Nome','Backend / Service Cookie / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookie','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Nome host','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Durata','Backend / Service Cookie / Table Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Nome</translation-key>','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Percorso','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Finalità','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineType'=>'Tipo','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineYou may input all cookies utilized by the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> here. Typically, information regarding which cookies are used and their respective purposes can be found on the website of the service you intend to add. For instance, details about the cookies used by Google Analytics can be located in its knowledge base.'=>'Puoi inserire qui tutti i cookie utilizzati dal <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. In genere, le informazioni relative ai cookie utilizzati e alle rispettive finalità sono reperibili sul sito web del servizio che si intende aggiungere. Ad esempio, i dettagli sui cookie utilizzati da Google Analytics possono trovarsi nella sua knowledge base.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key>?','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Spiegazione dei campi di input','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Description">Description</translation-key>: Enter a description of the cookie and explain its purpose. This is optional, but recommended.'=>'<translation-key id="Description">Descrizione</translation-key>: inserisci una descrizione del cookie e spiegane la finalità. È facoltativo, ma consigliato.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineThe <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser\'s developer tools can be used to find the values for the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>, and <translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key> fields.'=>'La sezione <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key> degli strumenti per sviluppatori del tuo browser può essere utilizzata per trovare i valori per i campi <translation-key id="Name">Nome</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Percorso</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Lifetime">Durata</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Inform your visitor how many days the cookie will be stored or enter <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> if the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when the browser is closed.'=>'<translation-key id="Lifetime">Durata</translation-key>: il campo corrisponde generalmente alla colonna <translation-key id="Expires">Scade</translation-key> della sezione <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key> del tuo browser. Informa il visitatore per quanti giorni il cookie sarà conservato o inserisci <translation-key id="Session">Sessione</translation-key> se il cookie è un cookie di sessione e sarà eliminato alla chiusura del browser.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find a date in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column, this means that the cookie is a persistent cookie and will be deleted on the specified date.'=>'Se nella colonna <translation-key id="Expires">Scade</translation-key> è presente una data, significa che il cookie è un cookie persistente e verrà eliminato alla data specificata.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find the value <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column of your browser, this means that the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when you close your browser.'=>'Se nella colonna <translation-key id="Expires">Scade</translation-key> del tuo browser è presente il valore <translation-key id="Session">Sessione</translation-key>, significa che il cookie è un cookie di sessione e verrà eliminato alla chiusura del browser.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Domain">Domain</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. You can enter <strong>#</strong> into this field and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will display the domain of your website in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key>: questo campo corrisponde generalmente alla colonna <translation-key id="Domain">Dominio</translation-key> nella sezione <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key> del tuo browser. Puoi inserire <strong>#</strong> in questo campo e <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> mostrerà il dominio del sito web nella <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser.'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Nome</translation-key>: il campo corrisponde generalmente alla colonna <translation-key id="Name">Nome</translation-key> nella sezione <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key> del tuo browser.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Usually, the path is <strong>/</strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Path">Percorso</translation-key>: il campo corrisponde generalmente alla colonna <translation-key id="Path">Percorso</translation-key> nella sezione <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookie</translation-key> del tuo browser. Di solito, il percorso è <strong>/</strong>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Purpose">Purpose</translation-key>: We distinguish in two types of <translation-key id="Purposes">Purposes</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Functional">Functional</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Purpose">Finalità</translation-key>: distinguiamo tra due tipi di <translation-key id="Purposes">Finalità</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Functional">Funzionalità</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Tracking">Tracciamento</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Functional">Functional</translation-key> cookies are required for the basic functionality of the website.'=>'I cookie di <translation-key id="Functional">Funzionalità</translation-key> sono necessari per la funzionalità di base del sito web.','Backend / Country / CountryNorway'=>'Norvegia','Backend / Library / Button TitleRefresh Library'=>'Aggiorna la libreria','Backend / Country / CountryNepal'=>'Nepal','Backend / Library / Button Title<translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstalla</translation-key>','Backend / Country / CountryNauru'=>'Nauru','Backend / Library / Button Title<translation-key id="Button-Uninstall">Uninstall</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Uninstall">Disinstalla</translation-key>','Backend / Country / CountryNiue'=>'Niue','Backend / Library / Button T