,'Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionSpecials'=>'Specials','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionZoom Entrances'=>'Zoom Entrances','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionZoom Exits'=>'Zoom Exits','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDatabase is downloaded'=>'Il database viene scaricato','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDatabase was not downloaded'=>'Il database non è stato scaricato','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDialog hidden'=>'Finestra di dialogo nascosta','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextLast Check with API'=>'Ultimo controllo con API','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDialog visible'=>'Finestra di dialogo visibile','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextYes, this feature is compatible with caching. To ensure functionality, please enable the <translation-key id="GeoIP-Caching-Mode">GeoIP Caching Mode</translation-key> option.'=>'Sì, questa funzione è compatibile con il caching. Per garantire la funzionalità, attiva l\'opzione <translation-key id="GeoIP-Caching-Mode">Modalità cache GeoIP</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> allows you show the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> only for visitors from some countries (e.g. for EU citizens).'=>'<translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> ti consente di mostrare la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> solo ai visitatori di alcuni Paesi (ad es. ai cittadini dell\'UE).','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextWhat is <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key>?'=>'Che cos\'è il <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key>?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextIs <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> working if your website uses caching?'=>'Il <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> funziona se il tuo sito web utilizza il caching?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineHow can the visitor change the consent?'=>'Come può il visitatore modificare il consenso?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineHow to display User ID, Consent History and Service &amp; Service Groups Overview.'=>'Come mostrare l\'ID utente, la cronologia dei consensi e il servizio &amp; panoramica dei gruppi di servizi.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineHow can the visitor perform an opt-out?'=>'Come può il visitatore effettuare un opt-in?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is <translation-key id="Service-Group-Justification">Service Group Justification</translation-key>?'=>'Che cos\'è la <translation-key id="Service-Group-Justification">Giustificazione del gruppo di servizi</translation-key>?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextTo offer this option, enter the following <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to your privacy page. This will create a button which reopens the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Per offrire questa opzione, inserisci il seguente <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> sulla tua pagina dell\'informativa sulla privacy. Questo creerà un pulsante che riapre la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextButton'=>'Pulsante','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextLink'=>'Link','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> below to display the <translation-key id=User-ID">User ID</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Utilizza lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> sottostante per mostrare l\'<translation-key id=User-ID">ID utente</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> below to display the <translation-key id="Consent-History">Consent History</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Utilizza lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> sottostante per mostrare la <translation-key id="Consent-History">Cronologia dei consensi</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> below to display an overview of all active <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Utilizza lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> sottostante per mostrare una panoramica di tutti i <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Gruppi di servizi</translation-key> attivi: {{ shortcode }}}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextInsert the following <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to your privacy page. This will create an opt-out button that allows the visitor to opt-out of the specified <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Inserisci il seguente <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> sulla tua pagina dell\'informativa sulla privacy. Questo creerà un pulsante opt-out che permetterà al visitatore di rinunciare al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> specificato: {{ shortcode }}}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextYou find the opt-out <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> for each <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Services</translation-key>. Click on a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, and you\'ll find the <translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Opt-out Shortcode</translation-key>.'=>'Puoi trovare lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> per l\'opt-out per ogni <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> sotto <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Servizi</translation-key>. Cliccando su un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>, troverai lo <translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Shortcode per l\'opt-out</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Justification-Around">Around</translation-key>: The spacing between each pair of adjacent items is the same. The empty space before the first and after the last item equals half of the space between each pair of adjacent items.'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Around">Intorno</translation-key>: la distanza tra ogni coppia di elementi adiacenti è la stessa. Lo spazio vuoto prima del primo e dopo l\'ultimo elemento è pari alla metà dello spazio tra ogni coppia di elementi adiacenti.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Justification-Between">Between</translation-key>: The spacing between each pair of adjacent items is the same. The first item is flush with the main-start edge, and the last item is flush with the main-end edge.'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Between">Tra</translation-key>: la distanza tra ogni coppia di elementi adiacenti è la stessa. Il primo elemento è a filo con il bordo principale di partenza e l\'ultimo elemento è a filo con il bordo principale di arrivo.','Backend / Country / CountryAndorra'=>'Andorra','Backend / Country / CountryUnited Arab Emirates'=>'Emirati Arabi Uniti','Backend / Country / CountryAfghanistan'=>'Afghanistan','Backend / Country / CountryAntigua and Barbuda'=>'Antigua e Barbuda','Backend / Country / CountryAnguilla'=>'Anguilla','Backend / Country / CountryAlbania'=>'Alba